727970f-b.title: Queens: Seagirt Avenue - Beach 17th Street
727970f-b.text:
Seagirt Ave., north side, between Beach 17th Street and Heyson
Road, showing in two views the Tackapausha Hotel located at the N.W.
corner of Heyson Road and Seagirt Ave. David Roach was the owner in
1891. The present hotel was erected upon the site of D. Roach's Union
Surf Hotel of 1873. Other owners were S. Metnger in 1899, and A. Hartman
in 1901.
October 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
